Package gg.sep.alyx.plugin.replies

Class EmbedReply

  • java.lang.Object
    • gg.sep.alyx.plugin.replies.EmbedReply
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ErrorReply, SuccessReply
    public class EmbedReply
extends java.lang.Object
    EmbedReply is a very basic helper class for modeling custom Discord Embed responses. This can be subclassed to customize its attributes.
